<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html>
<head>
    <title>Kindle Light轻小说</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="imagetoolbar" content="no" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/layout.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="icon/style.css" />
</head>

</head>



<body id="top">


    <%- include('head'); %>

    </div>

    <div class="wrapper col3">
        <div id="breadcrumb">
            <ul>
                <li class="first"><span class="icon-books"></span>欢迎来到Kindle Light 轻小说资源分享网！不会用？查看<a href="#">帮助</a></li>
                <li>||</li>
                <li><span class="icon-folder-download"></span>目前服务器的下载任务:<%= downListNum %></li>
                <li>||</li>
                <li><span class="icon-spinner6"></span>目前服务器的转换任务: <%= convListNum %></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="wrapper col3">
        <div id="breadcrumb">
            <ul>
                <li class="first"><span class="icon-newspaper"></span>公告：Hello!</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>



    <div class="wrapper col3">
        <div id="gallery">
            <h2>{ <span class="icon-clock"></span>最新更新 }</h2>
            <ul>


                <%# writing recent updated books %>

                <% recentBooks.forEach(function(e,i,a){ %>
                <li>
                    <a href="/book/<%=e.id%>"><img src="/book/cover/<%=e.id%>" width="200" height="300" /> </a>
                    <p align="center"><b><%=e.title%></b></p>
                    <p align="center">[<%=e.author%>]</p>
                    <p align="center">最后更新：<%= dateFormat(new Date(e.lastUpdate),"HH:MM yyyy-mm-dd") %> </p>

                </li>
                <%  }); %>

            </ul>
            <br class="clear" />
        </div>


        <div id="gallery">
            <h2>{ <span class="icon-bubbles4"></span>热门小说 }</h2>
            <ul>


                <%# writing recent updated books %>

                <% hotBooks.forEach(function(e,i,a){ %>
                <li>
                    <a href="/book/<%=e.id%>"><img src="/book/cover/<%=e.id%>" width="200" height="300" /> </a>
                    <p align="center"><b><%=e.title%></b></p>
                    <p align="center">[<%=e.author%>]</p>
                    <p align="center">热门度：<%=e.hotIndex%></p>

                </li>
                <%  }); %>

            </ul>
            <br class="clear" />
        </div>

        <div id="gallery">
            <h2>{ <span class="icon-lifebuoy"></span>随机小说 }</h2>
            <ul>


                <%# writing recent updated books %>

                <% randBooks.forEach(function(e,i,a){ %>
                <li>
                    <a href="/book/<%=e.id%>"><img src="/book/cover/<%=e.id%>" width="200" height="300" /> </a>
                    <p align="center"><b><%=e.title%></b></p>
                    <p align="center">[<%=e.author%>]</p>

                </li>
                <%  }); %>

            </ul>
            <br class="clear" />
        </div>



    </div>
    <div class="wrapper col4">
        <div id="container">
            <div id="content">
                <h2>{ 关于我们 }</h2>
                <p>所有内容均收集自互联网，本站只将资源进行转换并提供给同好交流。</p>
                <p>网站仅为写作爱好者及日语翻译学习交流提供试阅，如果你喜欢该作品，请购买正版支持.</p>
                <p>如无意中侵犯了您的著作权，请及时与我们联系，我们将在第一时间做出回应！</p>
            </div>
            <div id="column">
                <div class="flickrbox">
                    <h2 class="title">{ 关注我们 }</h2>
                    <ul>
                        
                    </ul>
                    <br class="clear" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <br class="clear" />
        </div>
    </div>


    <%- include('foot'); %>


</body>
</html>
